codex
The targeted suites are green (24/24), but they confirm control-flow output only; they do not exercise a transaction or inspect persisted PO/TO rows after the simulated second-group failure. I’m recording that as the blocking gap while distinguishing it from the implementation itself, whose throw paths are correctly placed.
